sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant REST as rest-proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as CustomJSONPb<br/>Decoder
    participant Encoder as CustomJSONPb<br/>Encoder
    participant GRPC as gRPC Client
    participant MM as ModelMesh gRPC<br/>8033/TCP (localhost)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,MM: Flow 1: REST-to-gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Optional TLS
        REST->>Decoder: JSON request body
        Note over Decoder: Transform JSON tensors<br/>to protobuf messages<br/>(BOOL, INT8-64, UINT8-64,<br/>FP32, FP64, BYTES)
        Decoder->>GRPC: ModelInfer protobuf request
        GRPC->>MM: gRPC ModelInfer RPC<br/>Optional TLS (localhost)
        MM-->>GRPC: ModelInferResponse protobuf
        GRPC-->>Encoder: protobuf response
        Note over Encoder: Transform protobuf tensors<br/>to JSON (including raw bytes<br/>and base64 BYTES tensors)
        Encoder-->>REST: JSON response body
        REST-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON response<br/>Optional TLS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,MM: Flow 2: Model Metadata Query
        Client->>REST: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>Optional TLS
        REST->>GRPC: ModelMetadata protobuf request
        GRPC->>MM: gRPC ModelMetadata RPC<br/>Optional TLS (localhost)
        MM-->>GRPC: ModelMetadataResponse protobuf
        GRPC-->>REST: JSON response
        REST-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON response<br/>Optional TLS
    end
